# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:4
translate french work0_f28cee14:

    # "Immediately after finishing up my classes for the day, I head out to the car and drive over to the Law Offices, where my new job is."
    "Dès que j'ai fini mes cours de la journée, je me dirige vers la voiture et je roule jusqu'au cabinet d'avocats, où se trouve mon nouveau travail."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:7
translate french work0_5a8d723c:

    # "I walk in to work. Dana is sitting in the lobby. I wave hello to her."
    "J'entre au travail. Dana est assise dans le hall. Je lui fais un signe de la main pour lui dire bonjour."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:8
translate french work0_468fc973:

    # cw "Hey there new guy. [pcname], wasn't it?"
    cw "Salut, le nouveau. [pcname], c'est bien ça ?"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:9
translate french work0_749220c3:

    # pc "That's me."
    pc "C'est moi."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:10
translate french work0_9e8ad45b:

    # cw "Mrs. Mills is back in her office. Go right ahead. Hope you have a good day."
    cw "Mme Mills est dans son bureau. Vas-y. Passe une bonne journée."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:11
translate french work0_efe7c8fa:

    # pc "Thanks, you too."
    pc "Merci, toi aussi."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:13
translate french work0_58488fe0:

    # "I go back to Mrs. Mills' office."
    "Je me rends dans le bureau de Mme Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:15
translate french work0_532a1db6:

    # "She sits at her desk, barely glancing up at me when I walk in."
    "Elle est assise à son bureau et lève à peine les yeux vers moi quand j'entre."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:17
translate french work0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_goodafternoon.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:18
translate french work0_640a0bfd:

    # bs "Good afternoon. I hope you're ready to work."
    bs "Bonjour. J'espère que tu es prêt à travailler."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:19
translate french work0_c24d08f6:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am, I am."
    pc "Oui, madame, je le suis."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:20
translate french work0_cc9bf2b9:

    # bs "Good."
    bs "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:22
translate french work0_4d725376:

    # "I spend most of the day cleaning. The place had gotten pretty bad over the few weeks where she didn't have an assistant and Mrs. Mills wants the place to be spotless."
    "Je passe la majeure partie de la journée à faire le ménage. L'endroit s'était bien dégradé au cours des quelques semaines où elle n'avait pas d'assistant, et Mme Mills veut que tout soit impeccable."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:23
translate french work0_e7ab64bb:

    # "I dust everything, wipe every surface, vacuum the floor, and organize all the paperwork."
    "Je dépoussière tout, j'essuie toutes les surfaces, je passe l'aspirateur et je range tous les documents."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:25
translate french work0_67f863e2:

    # "Afterwards, Mrs. Mills has me type all her notes while she dictates. Luckily, I'm a fast typist because she is a fast talker and doesn't slow down at all."
    "Ensuite, Mme Mills me demande de taper toutes ses notes pendant qu'elle dicte. Heureusement, je tape vite, car elle parle vite et ne ralentit pas du tout."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:26
translate french work0_cec5844a:

    # "Finally, when it is time to go, she looks over the notes that I had typed and gives a little nod."
    "Enfin, quand il est temps de partir, elle jette un œil aux notes que j’ai tapées et hoche légèrement la tête."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:30
translate french work0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:31
translate french work0_7e667a4e:

    # bs "You did good work today. Keep it up and maybe you'll be able to stick around here for a while."
    bs "Tu as bien travaillé aujourd’hui. Continue comme ça et tu pourras peut-être rester ici un moment."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:32
translate french work0_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "Merci."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:33
translate french work0_cd3b9566:

    # bs "See you tomorrow."
    bs "À demain."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:34
translate french work0_a5da4cbe:

    # pc "Okay, goodbye, Mrs. Mills."
    pc "D’accord, au revoir, Mme Mills."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:37
translate french work0_bab3cfa9:

    # "I walk out and down the hall to the lobby. There, Dana is still working, sorting paperwork at her desk."
    "Je sors et traverse le couloir jusqu’au hall d’entrée. Là, Dana est toujours au travail, en train de trier des papiers à son bureau."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:38
translate french work0_7c1acf53:

    # pc "Goodnight Dana."
    pc "Bonne nuit, Dana."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:40
translate french work0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_seeyoutomorrow.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:41
translate french work0_68df17d0:

    # cw "Oh, goodnight, [pcname]. See you tomorrow."
    cw "Oh, bonne nuit, [pcname]. À demain."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:43
translate french work0_ef83833d:

    # "I go outside and stand in front of the building for a moment, breathing the fresh air."
    "Je sors et je reste un moment devant l'immeuble, à respirer l'air frais."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:44
translate french work0_9dec6a30:

    # "It has been a long day and I'm exhausted. And this is only the first. Every weekday is going to be like this basically, leaving me only the evenings to do whatever I want."
    "La journée a été longue et je suis épuisée. Et ce n'est que le début. Tous les jours de la semaine vont se dérouler à peu près comme ça, ne me laissant que les soirées pour faire ce que je veux."

# game/Scenes/Work/work0.rpy:45
translate french work0_d7ac5816:

    # "So, what do I want to do now?"
    "Alors, qu'est-ce que j'ai envie de faire maintenant ?"

